<lb n="0038c10" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0038c11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0038c12" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1208</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0038c13" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0038009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">平安時代寫東寺寶菩提院三密藏藏本</note>俱力迦羅龍王儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0038c14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0038c15" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">金剛智三藏</byline>
<lb n="0038c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0038c1601">為此具最上利根人現身也。或為繫持念行
<lb n="0038c17" ed="T"/>者必可現形。是為大日如來因位三毒煩惱
<lb n="0038c18" ed="T"/>行相而已。</p>
<lb n="0038c19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0038c1901">爾時大日如來金剛忿怒力士諸天等。為我
<lb n="0038c20" ed="T"/>行者現忿怒龍王身。畏彼之三毒煩惱。永離
<lb n="0038c21" ed="T"/>三途輪迴苦業。此故可說我祕密&CB00057;。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0038c22" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0038c2201" type="dharani">&SD-E074;&SD-A67A;&SD-A5FD;&SD-CFC5;&SD-CFD3;&SD-A6B2;&SD-E05D;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0038c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0038c2301">次俱力迦羅龍王現身印真言。二手作忿怒
<lb n="0038c24" ed="T"/>奉舉二肩。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0038c25" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0038c2501" type="dharani">&SD-CFC5;&SD-A6B2;&SD-A67A;&SD-CFC1;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0038c26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0038c2601">次俱迦龍王不動明王真言印。二手金剛合
<lb n="0038c27" ed="T"/>掌。二火二空開散。二小指入掌中。真言。</p>
<lb n="0038c28" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0038c2801" type="dharani">&SD-E045;&SD-CFD4;&SD-A6A9;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0038c29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0038c2901">心中心印。內縛二水二火開散。心中心真言
<pb n="0039a" id="T21.1208.0039a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0039a01" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0039a02" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0039a0201" type="dharani">&SD-A6B3;&SD-AA5F;&SD-AB51;&SD-E05F;&SD-A662;&SD-CFC5;&SD-E05D;&SD-A55E;&SD-E045;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0039a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a0301">不動如來大日如來龍王現身根本真言</p>
<lb n="0039a04" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0039a0401" type="dharani">&SD-E074;&SD-AA5F;&SD-A656;&SD-A64A;&SD-A5EF;&SD-A6A6;&SD-CFC6;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0039a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a0501">誦此真言。必現身往生十方淨土。若拜尊容。
<lb n="0039a06" ed="T"/>至阿耨菩提終不墮三惡趣。此龍王火光三
<lb n="0039a07" ed="T"/>昧神通也。火天者此彼四智所語故。火天聖
<lb n="0039a08" ed="T"/>者火光三昧赫奕光明皆此火天身。能可念
<lb n="0039a09" ed="T"/>此龍王不思議神力。只有此法觀本生法變
<lb n="0039a10" ed="T"/>大日成不動變不動成劍之上相<term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</term>字返成龍
<lb n="0039a11" ed="T"/>王。左右無名小指掌內相叉。二中指直立相
<lb n="0039a12" ed="T"/>跓。以二食指跓中指背上節。以二大指小曲
<lb n="0039a13" ed="T"/>各柱二食指內中節來去。</p>
<lb n="0039a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a1401" type="dharani">曩莫三滿多勃馱南俱里迦耶迦羅惹銘伽扇
<lb n="0039a15" ed="T"/>&CB00135;曳娑婆訶</p>
<lb n="0039a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a1601">次俱力迦羅龍王密修真言印。內縛二中指。
<lb n="0039a17" ed="T"/>二大指開散<note place="inline">此密印也</note>。</p>
<lb n="0039a18" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0039a1801" type="dharani">&SD-A5A9;&SD-A5F0;&SD-A67A;&SD-A5E5;&SD-CA56;&SD-CFC1;&SD-E045;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0039a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a1901">次俱力迦羅變身印真言<note place="inline">大日如來也</note>。</p>
<lb n="0039a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2001">二手合掌。二風二空端相著。二水開立。真言
<lb n="0039a21" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0039a22" ed="T"/><p lang="san-sd" id="pT21p0039a2201" type="dharani">&SD-CFC5;&SD-A67A;&SD-A5E5;&SD-DA75;&SD-DA42;&SD-CFC1;&SD-A6A9;&SD-D5B4;</p>
<lb n="0039a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2301">次金剛體身真言印。</p>
<lb n="0039a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2401" type="dharani">唵唅吽&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉麼曳縛<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅
<lb n="0039a25" ed="T"/><term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</term></p>
<lb n="0039a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2601">次海三昧印真言。</p>
<lb n="0039a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2701" type="dharani">唵縛曰赦<term lang="san-sd">&SD-E045;&SD-CFC5;&SD-A94A;&SD-A6A9;&SD-CFC1;&SD-D5B4;</term></p>
<lb n="0039a28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2801">次常住火光三昧印真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0039a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039a2901" type="dharani">唵拔折羅赦悍<term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFD3;&SD-CFCD;&SD-A6A6;&SD-A6A9;&SD-D5B4;</term></p>
<pb n="0039b" id="T21.1208.0039b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0039b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b0101">若行者矞揭僮悀O迦龍王念。自然成護摩
<lb n="0039b02" ed="T"/>火光三昧。四臂明王皆此龍王用力常布行
<lb n="0039b03" ed="T"/>人身上阿字有其中劍遍含五字<term lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</term>。遍體成
<lb n="0039b04" ed="T"/>無動尊金剛身。如是觀已誦一字真言。</p>
<lb n="0039b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b0501" type="dharani">那莫三曼多&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅赦憾</p>
<lb n="0039b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b0601">次金迦羅印真言<note place="inline">釋迦此也</note>。</p>
<lb n="0039b07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b0701">印二手金剛合掌。二中指二大指入掌中即
<lb n="0039b08" ed="T"/>成真言。</p>
<lb n="0039b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b0901" type="dharani">唵金迦羅那&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅<term lang="san-sd">&SD-E1D7;</term></p>
<lb n="0039b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1001">次誓陀迦印真言。</p>
<lb n="0039b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1101">二手內縛。二地二風開散小曲相成。</p>
<lb n="0039b12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1201" type="dharani">唵&CB00085;<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>囉赦吽栖陀迦野娑婆賀</p>
<lb n="0039b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1301">次蓮花吉祥印真言<note place="inline">觀音是也部主</note>。</p>
<lb n="0039b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1401">二羽合掌。二水二風內相叉。</p>
<lb n="0039b15" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1501" type="dharani">曩莫三曼多縛<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】">日</lem><rdg wit="【大】">曰</rdg></app>羅赦吽吽憾曳陀羅野莎&CB01239;</p>
<lb n="0039b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0039b1601">此四使者加不動成五使者。大日如來五智
<lb n="0039b17" ed="T"/>成身此也。</p>
<lb n="0039b18" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>俱力迦羅儀軌</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>